\lim_{n\to\infty} x_n = a
\lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{nx_1 + (n-1)x_2 + \cdots + 2x_{n-1} + x_n}{n^2} = \frac{a}{2}.
y_n=nx_1+(n-1)x_2+\ldots+2x_{n-1}+x_n
y_{n+1}=(n+1)x_1+nx_2+(n-1)x_3+\ldots+2x_{n}+x_{n+1}
y_{n+1}-y_n=x_1+x_2+x_3+\ldots+x_n+x_{n+1}
(n+1)^2-n^2=n(2+1/n)
\frac{y_{n+1}-y_n}{(n+1)^2-n^2}-\frac{1}{2+1/n}\frac{x_1+x_2+x_3+\ldots+x_n+x_{n+1}}{n+1}\frac{n+1}{n} \to \frac{1}{2}.a.1=\frac{a}{2}.
